OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly low cloud, mist and fog
OL,6,Fwill lift to give some bright spells.
OL,7,FHowever, further low cloud, with mist
OL,8,Fand fog patches will gradually spread
OL,9,Facross the region from the west,
OL,10,Faccompanied by patchy rain. Feeling
OL,11,Fquite warm and humid.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will be a cloudy evening
OL,14,Fand night with mist and fog patches.
OL,15,FThere will be some patchy rain,
OL,16,Fturning locally heavier and more
OL,17,Fpersistent later. Warm and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
