OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloudy and murky during the
OL,6,Fmorning with some outbreaks of rain,
OL,7,Flocally heavy for a time. Becoming
OL,8,Fmostly dry during the afternoon with
OL,9,Fthe chance of a few brighter breaks.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FThe
OL,12,Fweather looks rather mixed to end the
OL,13,Fweek and start the weekend. Areas of
OL,14,Fcloud will give some rain at times,
OL,15,Fthough feeling warm in any brighter
OL,16,Fbreaks.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
